owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Absorption of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that has been incorporated into another resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Absorbed by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that incorporates another resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Accompanied by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that accompanies the described resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Accompanies
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that adds to or is issued with the described resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Source of acquisition
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information about an organization, person, etc., from which a resource may be obtained.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: should this be an annotation property? SES
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Administrative metadata
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Metadata about the metadata, especially provenance information.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: What *precisely* is an element of description?
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Associated agent
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Entity associated with a resource or element of description, such as the name of the entity responsible for the content or of the publication, printing, distribution, issue, release or production of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Applied material
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Physical or chemical substance applied to a base material of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Organization and arrangement
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information about the organization and arrangement of a collection of resources.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Aspect ratio
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Proportional relationship between an image's width and its height.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Assigner
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Entity that assigned the metadata, such as the entity that assigned a classification number, entity that assigned a name, entity that assigned an identifier.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Barcode
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Optical machine-readable representation of data relating to the item, to which it is attached.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Base material
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Underlying physical material of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Book format
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Result of folding a printed sheet to form a gathering of leaves.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Capture of content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information about place and date associated with the capture (e.g., recording, filming) of the content of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Carrier type
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting the format of the storage medium and housing of a carrier.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic data
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Cartographic data that identifies characteristics of the resource, such as coordinates, projection, etc.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Classification
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Classification number in any scheme.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Color content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Color characteristics, e.g., black and white, multicolored.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Content type
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting the fundamental form of communication in which the content is expressed and the human sense through which it is intended to be perceived.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Content accessibility information
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information that assists those with a sensory impairment for greater understanding of content, e.g., captions.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Continued by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource whose content continues an earlier resource under a new title.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Continued in part by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource part of whose content separated from an earlier resource to form a new resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Continuation of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is continued by the content of a later resource under a new title.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Continuation in part of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that split into two or more separate resources with new titles.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Contributor and role
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Agent and its role in relation to the resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Copyright registration information
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Copyright and Legal Deposit registration information

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Cover art
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Cover art image of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Data source
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is a data source to which the described resource is related. It may contain information about other files, printed sources, or collection procedures.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Is derivative of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Source work from which the described resource is derived.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Description authentication
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Indication of specific types of reviews that have been carried out on the description information.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Description conventions
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Rules used for the descriptive content of the resource description.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Description language
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Language used for the metadata.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Description modifier
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Agency that modified a description.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Digital characteristic
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Dissertation Information
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Work presented as part of the formal requirements for an academic degree.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: This should be a data property of type xsd:anyURI (SES)
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Electronic location
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Electronic location from which the resource is available.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Emulsion
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Suspension of light-sensitive chemicals used as a coating on a microfilm or microfiche, e.g., silver halide.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Ensemble
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Ensemble for which a musical work is appropriate.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Numbering or other enumeration and dates associated with issues or items held.
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Numbering and dates of issues or items held.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: This isn't be a sub-property of relatedTo (SES)
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Event content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Work whose content is the described event.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Has event content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Event that is the content of the described work.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Expression of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Work that the described Work is an expression of. For use to connect Works under FRBR/RDA rules.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Extent
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Number and type of units and/or subunits making up a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Finding aid
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Relationship for archival, visual, and manuscript resources to a finding aid or similar control materials.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Finding aid for
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Finding aid or similar control materials for archival, visual, and manuscript resources.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Font size
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Size of the type used to represent the characters and symbols in a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Frequency
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Intervals at which the parts of a serially produced resource or the updates to an integrating resource are issued.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Generation
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Relationship between an original carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Description generation
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Indication of the program or process used to generate the description by application of a particular transformation.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Genre/form
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Form category or genre to which a resource belongs

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Geographic coverage
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Geographic coverage of the content of the resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Degree issuing institution
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Name of degree granting institution.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Has derivative
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is a modification of the described work.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Equivalence
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource embodies the same content as the described resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Expressed as
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Work that is an expression of a described Work. For use to relate Works under FRBR/RDA rules.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Instance of Work
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Instance is related to described Work. For use to connect Works to Instances in the BIBFRAME structure.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Has holding
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Item which is an example of the described Instance.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Has part
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is included either physically or logically in the described resource

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Reproduced as
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that reproduces another Resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: In series
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource in which the part has been issued; the title of the larger resource appears on the part.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Subseries
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: series resource that is part of another series.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Held by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Entity holding the item or from which it is available.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Identifier
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Character string associated with a resource that serves to differentiate that resource from other resources, i.e., that uniquely identifies an entity.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Resouce identified
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is associated with a character string that serves to differentiate one resource from another.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Illustrative content information
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information about content intended to illustrate a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Immediate acquisition
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information about the circumstances, e.g., source, date, method, under which the resource was directly acquired.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Has index
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource has an accompanying index

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Index to
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Index that accompanies a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Instance of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Work the Instance described instantiates or manifests. For use to connect Instances to Works in the BIBFRAME structure.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Instrument
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Instrument for which a musical Work is appropriate.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Intended audience
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Information that identifies the specific audience or intellectual level for which the content of the resource is considered appropriate.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Mode of issuance
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting whether a resource is issued in one or more parts, the way it is updated, and its intended termination.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Issued with
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is issued on the same carrier as the resource being described.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Holding for
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Instance for which the described Item is an example.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Language information
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Language associated with a resource or its parts.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Layout
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, etc., in a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Media type
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting the general type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Merged to form
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: One of two or more resources that come together to form a new resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Merger of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: One of two or more resources which came together to form a new resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Mount material
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource has been attached.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Format of notated music
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Layout for content of a resource that is presented in the form of musical notation, such as full score, condensed score, vocal score, etc.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Music medium of performance
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Instrumental, vocal, and/or other medium of performance for which a musical resource was originally conceived, written or performed.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Notation system
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Alphabet, script, or symbol system used to convey the content of the resource, including specialized scripts, typefaces, tactile notation, movement notation, and musical notation.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Note
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: General textual information relating to a resource, such as Information about a specific copy of a resource or information about a particular attribute of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Associated title place
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Place from which the creation of the Work originated.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Original version
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource is the original version of which this resource is a reproduction.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Original version of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Original version of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Other edition
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource has other available editions, for example simultaneously published language editions or reprints.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Has other physical format
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is manifested in another physical carrier.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Is part of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource in which the described resource is physically or logically contained.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Place
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Geographic location or place entity associated with a resource or element of description, such as the place associated with the publication, printing, distribution, issue, release or production of a resource, place of an event.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Polarity
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Relationship of the colors and tones in an image to the colors and tones of the object reproduced.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Preceded by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that precedes the resource being described, e.g., is earlier in time or before in narrative.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Production method
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Process used to produce a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic projection
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Method or system used to represent the surface of the earth or of a celestial sphere on a plane.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Projection characteristic
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the projection of a motion picture film.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Provision activity
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Place, name, and/or date information relating to the publication, printing, distribution, issue, release, production, etc. of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Reduction ratio
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Size of a micro-image in relation to the original from which it was produced.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Referenced by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that references the described resource

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Expected value Work, Instance or Item
Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: References
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is referenced by the described resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Related resource
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Any relationship between Work, Instance, and Item resources.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Succeeded by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Later resource used in place of an earlier resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Preceded by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Earlier resource whose content has been replaced by a later resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Reproduction of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is a reproduction of another Resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Review content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Review of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.dcterms:modified: 2017-02-03 (Changed from data to object property, adjusted label and definition)
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Contributor role
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Function provided by a contributor, e.g., author, illustrator, etc.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Scale
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Ratio of the dimensions of a form contained or embodied in a resource to the dimensions of the entity it represents, e.g., for images or cartographic resources.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Separated from
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that spun off a part of its content to form a new resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Series container of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is a part of a larger resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Shelf mark
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Piece identifier, such as a call or other type of number.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Sound characteristic
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the encoding of sound in a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Sound content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Indication of whether the production of sound is an integral part of the resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: What is meant by value or label here? (SES)
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Source
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource from which value or label came or was derived, such as the formal source/scheme from which a classification number is taken or derived, list from which an agent name is taken or derived, source within which an identifier is unique.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Split into
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: One of two or more resources resulting from the division of an earlier resource into separate resources.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Status
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Designation of the validity or position of something, such as indication that the classification number is canceled or invalid, circulation availability of an item, indication of whether the identifier is canceled or invalid.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Subject
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Subject term(s) describing a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Held in sublocation
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Specific place within the holding entity where the item is located or made available.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Subseries of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Series resource of which the described resource is a part.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Succeeded by
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that succeeds the resource being described, e.g., later in time or after in a narrative.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Summary content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Summary or abstract of the resource described.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Supplement
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that updates or otherwise complements the predominant resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Supplement to
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that is updated or otherwise complemented by the augmenting resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Supplementary material
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Material such as an index, bibliography, appendix intended to supplement the primary content of a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.dcterms:modified: 2017-02-06 (Changed from data to object property, changed property name from plural to singular)
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Equipment or system requirements
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Equipment or system requirement beyond what is normal and obvious for the type of carrier or type of file, such as make and model of equipment or hardware, operating system, amount of memory, programming language, other necessary software, any plug-ins or peripherals required to play, view, or run the resource, etc.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Table of contents content
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Table of contents of the described resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Title resource
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Name given to a resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Translation as
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that translates the text of the source entity into a language different from that of the original.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Translation of
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Resource that has been translated, i.e., the text is expressed in a language different from that of the original resource.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Where are these values? What are these values? (SES)
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Type of unit
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Units in which a value is expressed, such as the physical or logical constituent of a resource (e.g., a volume, audiocassette, film reel, a map, a digital file).

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Use and access condition
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: General statement of allowances and restrictions on access to a resource, including retention, reproduction, access, and lending.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Video characteristic
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the encoding of video images in a resource

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Voice
owl:ObjectProperty.skos:definition: Voice for which a musical work is appropriate, such as soprano, tenor, mixed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Terms of acquisition
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Conditions under which the publisher, distributor, etc., will normally supply a resource, e.g., price of a resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic ascension and declination
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: System for identifying the location of a celestial object in the sky covered by the cartographic content of a resource using the angles of right ascension and declination.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Award note
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Information on awards associated with the described resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Description change date
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date or date and time on which the metadata was modified.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Classification number (single class number or beginning number of a span) that indicates the subject by applying a formal system of coding and organizing resources.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Code
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: String of characters that serves as a code representing information.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic coordinates
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Mathematical system for identifying the area covered by the cartographic content of a resource, expressed either by means of longitude and latitude on the surface of planets or by the angles of right ascension and declination for celestial cartographic content.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Copyright date
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date associated with a claim of protection under copyright or a similar regime.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Shouldn't the number of units be some number type? (SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Number of units
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Number associated with a measure of units, such as the number of units and/or subunits making up a resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Description creation date
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date or date and time on which the original metadata first created.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Credits note
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Information in note form of credits for persons or organizations who have participated in the creation and/or production of the resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Used with Work, Instance or Item
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Custodial history
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Information about the provenance, such as origin, ownership and custodial history (chain of custody), of a resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Date
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date designation associated with a resource or element of description, such as date of title variation; year a degree was awarded; date associated with the publication, printing, distribution, issue, release or production of a resource. May be date typed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Degree
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Degree for which author was a candidate.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Source metadata
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Link to the metadata that was the source of the data.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Dimensions
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Measurements of the carrier or carriers and/or the container of a resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: ideally this would be an xsd:duration, but that's non-standard(SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Duration
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Information about the playing time, running time, etc. of a resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: This could be an object property, with a range that is enumerated
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification scheme edition
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Edition of the classification scheme, such as full, abridged or a number, when a classification scheme designates editions.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Edition enumeration
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Enumeration of the edition; usually transcribed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Edition statement
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Information identifying the edition or version of the resource and associated statements of responsibility for the edition; usually transcribed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: This is the sort of property that should be an *Objec*t property, with a range Class that has Orchestra, band, etc, as Individuals. (SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Ensemble type
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Specific type of ensemble, such as orchestra, band, guitar ensemble.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Sounds like this could be an object property with a class with two values?
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic equinox
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: One of two points of intersection of the ecliptic and the celestial equator, occupied by the sun when its declination is 0 degrees.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic G ring area excluded
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Coordinate pairs that identify the closed non-intersecting boundary of the area contained within the G-polygon outer ring that is excluded.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Multipart first issue
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Beginning date of a resource and/or the sequential designations.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Date generated
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date of conversion of the metadata from another format.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Hierarchical level of material
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Hierarchical position of the described materials relative to other material from the same source.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: History of the work
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Information about the history of a Work.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Instrument role
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Specific role of instrument, such as alternate, doubling, solo, ensemble.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification item number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Number attached to a classification string that indicates a particular item.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Multipart last issue
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Ending date of a resource and/or the sequential designations.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Date of legal work
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date of legal work, or promulgation of a law, or signing of a treaty.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Main title
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Title being addressed. Possible title component.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Music key
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Pitch and mode for music.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Music opus number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Numeric designation of a musical work assigned by a composer, publisher, or a musicologist.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: What kind of number? Why not a number type?(SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Music serial number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Numeric designation for musical works consecutively numbered in music reference sources.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Music thematic number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Numeric designation for a musical work as found in a thematic index for the composer.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Are these all ad-hoc? If not, why isn't this an object property with a range class for the values? Or possibly a class hierarchy? (SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Content nature
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Characterization that epitomizes the primary content of a resource, e.g., field recording of birdsong; combined time series analysis and graph plotting system.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Why is the type of note not a type? (SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Note type
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Type of note.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Organization of material
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Manner in which the resource is divided into smaller units.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Associated title date
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Date or date range associated with the creation of a Work.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Cartographic outer G ring area covered
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Coordinate pairs that identify the closed non-intersecting boundary of the area covered.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: What does this property do? It seems like resource is used elsewhere to refer to some of subset of Work , Instance and Item? But this is a data property. What information? (SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Part
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Part of a resource to which information applies.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Part title
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Part or section name of a title. Possible title component.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Part number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Part or section enumeration of a title. Possible title component.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Arrangement of material
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Pattern of arrangement of materials within a unit.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Storing or shelving location
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Location in the holding agency where the item is shelved or stored.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Preferred citation
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Citation to the resource preferred by its custodian of the resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Provider statement
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Statement relating to providers of a resource; usually transcribed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: Void for vagueness. Domain Thing, Range Literal, meaning: some sort of extra information associated with some other information? (SES)
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Qualifier
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Qualifier of information, such as an addition to a title to make it unique or qualifying information associated with an identifier.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Creative responsibility statement
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Statement relating to any persons, families, or corporate bodies responsible for the creation of, or contributing to the content of a resource; usually transcribed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification designation
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Designates whether the classification number is from the standard or optional part of a schedule or table.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Series enumeration
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Series enumeration of the resource; usually transcribed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Series statement
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Statement of the series the resource is in; usually transcribed; includes the ISSN if applicable.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification number span end
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Ending number of classification number span.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Subseries enumeration
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Subseries enumeration of the resource; usually transcribed.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Subseries statement
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Statement of the subseries the resource is in; usually transcribed; includes the ISSN if applicable.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Subtitle
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Word, character, or group of words and/or characters that contains the remainder of the title after the main title. Possible title component.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification table identification
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Number of the table from which the classification number in a subdivision entry is taken, e.g., a DDC table.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Classification table sequence number
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Sequence number or other identifier for an internal classification sub arrangement or add in a classification scheme.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Temporal coverage
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Time period coverage of the content of the resource.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Variant title type
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Type of title variation, e.g., acronym, cover, spine, earlier, later, series version.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Version
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Term or terms that identify works such as arranged for music, vulgate for religious work, etc.

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Type of voice
owl:DatatypeProperty.skos:definition: Specific type of voice group, such as chorus, solo.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Abbreviated title
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title as abbreviated for citation, indexing, and/or identification.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Access policy
owl:Class.skos:definition: Access restrictions and allowances regarding access to a resource, e.g., lending policy, access restrictions, embargos.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Acquisition source
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about an organization, person, etc., from which a resource may be obtained.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Administrative metadata
owl:Class.skos:definition: Metadata about the metadata, especially provenance information.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Agent
owl:Class.skos:definition: Entity having a role in a resource, such as a person or organization.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ANSI number
owl:Class.skos:definition: American National Standards Institute identifier.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Applied material
owl:Class.skos:definition: Physical or chemical substance applied to a base material of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Archival controlled
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resources organically created, accumulated, and/or used by a person, family, or organization in the course of conduct of affairs and preserved because of their continuing value.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Organization of materials information
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about the organization and arrangement of a collection of items. For instance, for computer files, organization and arrangement information may be the file structure and sort sequence of a file; for visual materials, this information may be how a collection is arranged.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Aspect ratio
owl:Class.skos:definition: Proportional relationship between an image's width and its height.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Audio
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resources expressed in an audible form, including music or other sounds.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Audio issue number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number assigned by publishers of sound recordings to identify the issue designation, or serial identification, of the resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Audio recording take
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier assigned to the smallest identifiable unit of a recording session, e.g., a specific recording of an individual song.

owl:Class.dcterms:modified: 2017-02-03 (Moved to Identifier class group from Item group)
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Barcode
owl:Class.skos:definition: Optical machine-readable representation of data relating to the item to which it is attached.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Base material
owl:Class.skos:definition: Underlying physical material of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Book format
owl:Class.skos:definition: Result of folding a printed sheet to form a gathering of leaves.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Broadcast standard
owl:Class.skos:definition: System used to format a video resource for television broadcast, e.g., HDTV, PAL.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Capture of content
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about place and date associated with the capture (i.e., recording, filming, etc.) of the content of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Carrier type
owl:Class.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting the format of the storage medium and housing of a carrier.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cartographic information
owl:Class.skos:definition: Content that represents the whole or part of the earth, any celestial body, or imaginary place at any scale.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Digital cartographic data type
owl:Class.skos:definition: Data type for encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource, e.g., raster, vector, point.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Digital cartographic object type
owl:Class.skos:definition: Object type for encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource, e.g., point, line, polygon.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cartography
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource that shows spatial information, including maps, atlases, globes, digital, and other cartographic resources.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Chronology
owl:Class.skos:definition: Dates associated with issues or items held.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Classification entity
owl:Class.skos:definition: System of coding and organizing materials according to their subject.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: DDC Classification
owl:Class.skos:definition: Dewey Decimal Classification number used for subject access.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: LCC Classification
owl:Class.skos:definition: Library of Congress Classification number used for subject access.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: NLM classification
owl:Class.skos:definition: National Library of Medicine Classification number used for subject access

owl:Class.rdfs:label: UDC Classification
owl:Class.skos:definition: Universal Decimal Classification number used for subject access.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: CODEN
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier for scientific and technical periodical titles assigned by the International CODEN Section of Chemical Abstracts Service.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Collection
owl:Class.skos:definition: Aggregation of resources, generally gathered together artificially.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Collective title
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title for a compilation of resources.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Color content
owl:Class.skos:definition: Color characteristics of a resource, e.g., black and white, multicolored, etc.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Content type
owl:Class.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting the fundamental form of communication in which the content is expressed and the human sense through which it is intended to be perceived.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Content accessibility information
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information that assists those with a sensory impairment for greater understanding of content, e.g., captions.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Contribution
owl:Class.skos:definition: Agent and role with respect to the resource being described.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Copyright-legal deposit number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier assigned to a copyright registration or legal deposit.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Copyright registration
owl:Class.skos:definition: Copyright or Legal Deposit registration information

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Cover art
owl:Class.skos:definition: Cover illustration of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Dataset
owl:Class.skos:definition: Data encoded in a defined structure. Includes numeric data, environmental data,etc., used by applications software to calculate averages, correlations, etc., or to produce models, etc., but not normally displayed in its raw form.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Metadata authentication
owl:Class.skos:definition: Indication of specific types of reviews that have been carried out on the description information.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Description conventions
owl:Class.skos:definition: Rules used for the descriptive content of the resource description.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Digital characteristic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Dissertation information
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about a work presented as part of the formal requirements for an academic degree.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Dissertation Identifier
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier assigned to a thesis or dissertation for identification purposes .

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Distributor
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information relating to distribution of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: DOI
owl:Class.skos:definition: Digital Object Identifier.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: EAN
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Article Identifier.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Electronic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource that is intended for manipulation by a computer, accessed either directly or remotely.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Emulsion
owl:Class.skos:definition: Suspension of light-sensitive chemicals used as a coating on a microfilm or microfiche, e.g., silver halide.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Encoded bitrate
owl:Class.skos:definition: Speed at which streaming audio, video, etc., is designed to play, e.g., 32 kbps.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Encoding format
owl:Class.skos:definition: Schema, standard, etc., used to encode the digital content of a resource, e.g., MP3, XML, JPEG.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Enumeration
owl:Class.skos:definition: Numbering or other enumeration associated with issues or items held.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Enumeration and chronology
owl:Class.skos:definition: Numbering or other enumeration and dates associated with issues or items held.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Event entity
owl:Class.skos:definition: Something that happens at a certain time and location, such as a performance, speech, or athletic event, that is documented by a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Extent
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number and type of units and/or subunits making up a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Family
owl:Class.skos:definition: Two or more persons related by birth, marriage, adoption, civil union, or similar legal status, or who otherwise present themselves as a family.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: File size
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number of bytes in a digital file, e.g., 162 KB.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: File type
owl:Class.skos:definition: General type of data content encoded in a computer file, e.g., text file, audio file.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Fingerprint identifier
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier that is used to assist in the identification of antiquarian books by recording information comprising groups of characters taken from specified positions on specified pages of the book.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Font size
owl:Class.skos:definition: Size of the type used to represent the characters and symbols in a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Frequency
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about intervals at which the parts of a serially produced resource or the updates to an integrating resource are issued.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Generation
owl:Class.skos:definition: Relationship between an original carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Generation process
owl:Class.skos:definition: Indication of the program or process used to generate the description by application of a particular transformation.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Genre/form
owl:Class.skos:definition: Characteristics of works with similar plots, themes, settings, etc. (e.g., westerns, thrillers), or with a particular format of purpose (e.g., animation, short), or a combination (e.g., horror film where horror is the genre and film is the form).

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Geographic coverage
owl:Class.skos:definition: Geographic coverage of the content of the resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Groove characteristic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Groove width of an analog disc or the groove pitch of an analog cylinder, e.g., coarse groove, microgroove

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Global Trade Item Number 14
owl:Class.skos:definition: 14 digit number assigned to identify trade items as various packaging levels. GTIN-14 encompasses EAN/UCC-128 and ITF-14.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Handle
owl:Class.skos:definition: Unique and persistent identifier for digital objects developed by the Corporation for National Research Initiatives.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Identifier
owl:Class.skos:definition: Token or name that is associated with a resource, such as a URI or an ISBN.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Illustrative content
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about content intended to illustrate a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Immediate acquisition
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about the circumstances, e.g., source, date, method, under which the resource was directly acquired.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Instance
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource reflecting an individual, material embodiment of a Work.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Instance title
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title chosen as the name of an Instance, sometimes called "title proper" and often transcribed from the instance.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Intended audience information
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information that identifies the specific intended or target audience or intellectual level for which the content described is considered appropriate. Also used to record interest and motivation levels and special learner characteristics.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISAN
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Audiovisual Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISBN
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Book Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISMN
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Music Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISNI
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Name Identifier, a unique, persistent reference number for the identities of contributors to creative works.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISO number
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Organization for Standardization standard number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISRC
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Recording Code.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISSN
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Serial Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISSN-L
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Serial Number that links together various media versions of a continuing resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Mode of issuance
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about whether a resource is issued in one or more parts, the way it is updated, and its intended termination.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISTC
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Text Code, a numbering system developed to enable the unique identification of textual works.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: ISWC
owl:Class.skos:definition: International Standard Musical Work Code, a unique, persistent reference number for the identification of musical works.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Item
owl:Class.skos:definition: Single example of an Instance.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Jurisdiction
owl:Class.skos:definition: Legal or political unit administering a geographic area.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Key title
owl:Class.skos:definition: Unique title for a continuing resource that is assigned by the ISSN International Center in conjunction with an ISSN.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Language entity
owl:Class.skos:definition: Language entity.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Layout
owl:Class.skos:definition: Arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, etc., in a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: LC acquisition program
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identification number assigned by the Library of Congress to works acquired through one of its collaborative overseas acquisition programs.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: LCCN
owl:Class.skos:definition: Library of Congress Control Number that identifies a resource description.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Local identifier
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier established locally and not a standard number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Manufacturer
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information relating to manufacture of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Manuscript
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource that is written in handwriting or typescript. These are generally unique resources.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Audio matrix number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Matrix identifier assigned to the master from which a specific sound recording was pressed.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Media type
owl:Class.skos:definition: Categorization reflecting the general type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Meeting
owl:Class.skos:definition: Gathering of individuals or representatives of various bodies for the purpose of discussing and/or acting on topics of common interest.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Mixed material
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource comprised of multiple types which are not driven by software. This may include materials in two or more forms that are related by virtue of their having been accumulated by or about a person or body., archival fonds.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Mount
owl:Class.skos:definition: Physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource has been attached.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Movement notation used
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information on the symbol system used to convey the content of a movement resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Moving image
owl:Class.skos:definition: Images intended to be perceived as moving, including motion pictures (using liveaction and/or animation), video recordings of performances, events,etc.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Software or multimedia
owl:Class.skos:definition: Electronic resource that is a computer program (i.e., digitally encoded instructions intended to be processed and performed by a computer) or which consists of multiple media types that are software driven, such as videogames.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music distributor number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier appearing on a resource assigned by a distributor to a specific audio recording, notated music publication, music-related publication, or videorecording.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music ensemble
owl:Class.skos:definition: Ensemble for which a musical work is appropriate.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Notated music format
owl:Class.skos:definition: Layout for content of a resource that is presented in the form of musical notation.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Musical instrument
owl:Class.skos:definition: Instrument for which a musical work is appropriate.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music medium information
owl:Class.skos:definition: Summary statement of the medium for a musical work.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music notation used
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information on the symbol system used to convey the content of a music resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music plate number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifiers assigned by a music publisher or printer to the printing plates for the notated portion of a notated music publication, or an identifier that emulates the printing plate tradition in contemporary publications.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music publisher number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identifier assigned to a notated music publication other than an issue, matrix, or plate number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Music voice
owl:Class.skos:definition: Voice for which a musical work is appropriate.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: NBN
owl:Class.skos:definition: National Bibliography Number that identifies a resource description.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Notated movement
owl:Class.skos:definition: Graphic, non-realized representations of movement intended to be perceived visually, e.g. dance.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Notated music
owl:Class.skos:definition: Graphic, non-realized representations of musical works intended to be perceived visually.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Notation
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information on the alphabet, script, or symbol system used to convey the content of the resource, including specialized scripts, typefaces, tactile notation, movement notation, and musical notation.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Note
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information, usually in textual form, on attributes of a resource or some aspect of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Three-dimensional object
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource in a form intended to be perceived visually in three-dimensions. Includes man-made objects such as models, sculptures, clothing, and toys, as well as naturally occurring objects such as specimens mounted for viewing.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Digital cartographic object count
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number of objects in encoded geospatial information in a cartographic resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Organization
owl:Class.skos:definition: Corporation or group of persons and/or organizations that acts, or may act, as a unit.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Parallel title proper
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title in another language and/or script.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Person
owl:Class.skos:definition: Individual or identity established by an individual (either alone or in collaboration with one or more other individuals).

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Place
owl:Class.skos:definition: Geographic location.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Configuration of playback channels
owl:Class.skos:definition: Configuration/number of sound channels used to make a recording, such as one channel for a monophonic recording, e.g., mono, stereo, quadraphonic, surround.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Special playback characteristics
owl:Class.skos:definition: Equalization system, noise reduction system, etc., used in making an audio recording, e.g., CCIR standard, CX encoded, Dolby.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Playing speed
owl:Class.skos:definition: Speed at which an audio carrier must be operated to produce the sound intended, e.g., 78 rpm, 19 cm/s.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Polarity
owl:Class.skos:definition: Relationship of the colors and tones in an image to the colors and tones of the object reproduced.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Postal registration number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number assigned to a publication for which the specified postal service permits the use of a special mailing class privilege.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Presentation format
owl:Class.skos:definition: Format used in the production of a projected image, e.g., Cinerama, IMAX.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Printed
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource that is printed.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Producer
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information relating to production of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Production method
owl:Class.skos:definition: Process used to produce a resource

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Projection
owl:Class.skos:definition: Method or system used to represent the surface of the earth or of a celestial sphere on a plane.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Projection characteristic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the projection of a motion picture film.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Projection speed
owl:Class.skos:definition: Speed at which a projected carrier must be operated to produce the moving image intended, e.g., 20 fps.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Provider entity
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information about the agent or place relating to the publication, printing, distribution, issue, release, or production of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Publisher
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information relating to publication of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Other publisher number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number assigned by a publisher that is not one of the specific defined types.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Recording medium
owl:Class.skos:definition: Type of medium used to record sound on an audio carrier, e.g., magnetic, optical.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Type of recording
owl:Class.skos:definition: Method used to encode audio content for playback, e.g., analog, digital.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Reduction ratio
owl:Class.skos:definition: Size of a micro-image in relation to the original from which it was produced.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Regional encoding
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identification of the region of the world for which a videodisc has been encoded, e.g., region 4.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Technical report number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identification number of a technical report that is not a Standard Technical Report Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Resolution
owl:Class.skos:definition: Clarity or fineness of detail in a digital image, expressed by the measurement of the image in pixels, etc., e.g., 3.1 megapixels.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Retention policy
owl:Class.skos:definition: Policy of holding institution for retaining resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Review
owl:Class.skos:definition: Review of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Role
owl:Class.skos:definition: Function played or provided by a contributor, e.g., author, illustrator, etc.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Scale
owl:Class.skos:definition: Ratio of the dimensions of a form contained or embodied in a resource to the dimensions of the entity it represents, e.g., for images or cartographic resources.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Script used
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information on the script, or symbol system used to convey the content of a text resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Shelf location
owl:Class.skos:definition: Piece/item identifier, such as a call or other type of number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: DDC call number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Shelf mark based on Dewey Decimal Classification.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: LCC call number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Shelf mark based on Library of Congress Classification.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: NLM call number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Shelf mark based on National Library of Medicine Classification.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: UDC call number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Shelf mark based on Universal Decimal Classification.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: SICI
owl:Class.skos:definition: Serial Item and Contribution Identifier.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Sound characteristic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the encoding of sound in a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Sound content
owl:Class.skos:definition: Indication of whether the production of sound is an integral part of the resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Source
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource from which value or label came or was derived.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Status
owl:Class.skos:definition: Designation of the validity or position of something, e.g., whether something is incorrect or available.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Still image
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource expressed through line, shape, shading, etc., intended to be perceived visually as a still image or images in two dimensions. Includes two-dimensional images and slides and transparencies.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Stock number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identification number used for stock purposes and assigned by agencies such as distributors, publishers, or vendors.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: STRN
owl:Class.skos:definition: Standard Technical Report Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Study number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Identification number for a computer data file.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Sublocation
owl:Class.skos:definition: Specific place within the holding entity where the item is located or made available.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Summary
owl:Class.skos:definition: Description of the content of a resource, such as an abstract, summary, etc..

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Supplementary material
owl:Class.skos:definition: Index, bibliography, appendix, etc. intended to supplement the primary content of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: System Requirement
owl:Class.skos:definition: Equipment or system requirements beyond what is normal and obvious for the type of carrier or type of file, such as make and model of equipment or hardware, operating system, amount of memory, programming language, other necessary software, any plug-ins or peripherals required to play, view, or run the resource, etc.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Table of contents
owl:Class.skos:definition: Table of contents of a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Tactile material
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource that is intended to be perceived by touch.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Tactile notation used
owl:Class.skos:definition: Information on the symbol system used to convey the content of a tactile resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Tape configuration
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number of tracks on an audiotape, e.g., 12 track.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Temporal concept
owl:Class.skos:definition: Chronological period.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Text
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource intended to be perceived visually and understood through the use of language in written or spoken form.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Title entity
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title information relating to a resource: work title, preferred title, instance title, transcribed title, translated title, variant form of title, etc.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Topic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Concept or area of knowledge.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Track configuration
owl:Class.skos:definition: Configuration of the audio track on a sound-track film, e.g., center track, edge track.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Unit
owl:Class.skos:definition: Units in which a value is expressed.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: UPC
owl:Class.skos:definition: Universal Product Code.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: URN
owl:Class.skos:definition: Uniform Resource Number.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Use and access conditions
owl:Class.skos:definition: General statement of allowances and restrictions on access to a resource, including retention, reproduction, access, and lending.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Use policy
owl:Class.skos:definition: Usage limitations placed on a resource with respect to reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc..

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Title variation
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title associated with the resource that is different from the Work or Instance title.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Video characteristic
owl:Class.skos:definition: Technical specification relating to the encoding of video images in a resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Video format
owl:Class.skos:definition: Standard, etc., used to encode the analog video content of a resource, e.g., Beta, 8mm.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Video recording number
owl:Class.skos:definition: Number assigned by a publisher to a video recording.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Work
owl:Class.skos:definition: Resource reflecting a conceptual essence of a cataloging resource.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Work title
owl:Class.skos:definition: Title or form of title chosen to identify the work, such as a preferred title, preferred title with additions, uniform title, etc.
